title: ~ A STATE OF TRANCE #000 - #350 ~ THE COMPLETE COLLECTION
description:
THE COMPLETE COLLECTION OF ARMIN VAN BUUREN&#039;S RADIOSHOW

~ A STATE OF TRANCE ~

EPISODES #000 - #350.

I also included a pdf-file containing all the tracklistings #000 - #350.

For everyone&#039;s convenience, I did not pack the episodes in a huge zip or rar file.
So it is up to you what episode(s) you want to download or not.

My goal is:
- to provide the new fans with all the episodes that have been broadcasted so far (until the 1st. of May 2008);
- to enable all the other fans to complete their collections by enable them to just download their missing episodes;
- to provide for one single document with all the tracklistings.

There are three parts missing in the entire collection. I could not find them so far... :-(

Maybe someone else can help me? I would like to lay my hands on:
- Episode 001 - Part 1 (aired on June 1st. 2001)
- Episode 004 - Part 1 (aired on June 22nd. 2001)
- Episode 020 - Part 2 (aired on November 1st. 2001)

Please seed and keep seeding during and after downloading.

Enjoy... :-)
